    "attributes": {
        "action": "Reduce maximum stake Fixed Odds Betting Terminals from \u00a3100 to \u00a32 by April 2019",
        "additional_details": "\"From the time of the announcement to reduce stakes and its implementation, over \u00a31.6bn will be lost on these machines\u201d\r\n\r\n\"In addition, two people will tragically take their lives every day due to gambling-related problems and, for that reason as much as any other, I believe this delay is unjustifiable.\" - Tracey Couch\r\n\r\nProblem gamblers are often troubled, vulnerable and in self-destruct mode. An addict desires to burn quickly - the 'crack-cocaine' FOBT machines facilitate this B2 gaming/roulette can take \u00a3100 in seconds.\r\n\r\nPlease sign this petition to reduce the misery and risk of losing a loved one",
        "background": "Chancellor Philip Hammond said in Monday's Budget that the in stakes from \u00a3100 to \u00a32 would come into force in October 2019 not the agreed April 2019, this is totally unacceptable\r\n\r\nThe users of these machines are being sacrificed over Gambling Industry Profits.",
